Up-to-date, in-depth knowledge of modern web technologies: HTML5, CSS3, JS, AngularJS, NodeJS, React
Ability to do full-stack is a plus
Experience with Bootstrap, responsive design
Solid understanding of cross browsers/cross platforms compatibility issues
